{"tid":665845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拖鞋男涉請食糖誘狎女童","createTime":"2018-05-15T10:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T14:53:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"22e1f3d4dd7a7ce86dee9759c71842e632a90ba7","tid":665845,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:22:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180515/20391463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20391463&d=fPrERKXOLSGnjnJt4dppo%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=fe95da6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20391463&h=676e3694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180515/20391463</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月15日 <br />\n<br />\n拖鞋男涉請食糖誘狎女童<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180515/large/18087348.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F18087348.jpg&h=1874784f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■將軍澳新都城去年暑假發生6歲女童疑遭拖鞋色魔非禮案，案件昨在區域法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】將軍澳新都城去年暑假發生6歲女童疑遭拖鞋色魔非禮案，涉案一名在台灣讀大學的男生翌日向警方投案，被控非禮罪，案件昨在區域法院開審。女童指當日在商場平台踏單車，遭被告請食糖誘至商場男廁，要她小便給他看，又舐她的下體，事後還稱這是兩人之間的秘密，跟她勾手指尾着她不要告知任何人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nX稱被要求勾手指尾守秘<br />\n<br />\n根據女童X的錄影會面，X於去年8月28日與家傭到新都城商場平台踩單車，後來遇到一位穿拖鞋、不認識的「哥哥」，對方聲稱她的家傭帶了她兄長去買餸，故「姐姐叫我同你玩」，又請她吃糖，着她跟他往男廁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nX指「哥哥」將她帶到商場男廁廁格，「叫我屙尿畀佢睇」。X照做，「哥哥」又舐她下體一會兒，令她有「少少痛」。「哥哥」最後逼她吻其面，又稱「呢啲係我同你之間嘅秘密，唔可以講畀人知」，還跟她勾手指尾。稍後他帶X返平台，再逼她跟他親吻。<br />\n臨離開前，「哥哥」着她翌日再往找他，會請她吃糖，女童隨家傭回家後將事告訴外婆揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\nX後來在列隊認人中認出「哥哥」就是被告李健聰（25歲）。被告在警誡下稱只是請女童吃糖，並帶她往洗手間，之後用紙巾替她抹下體。<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨盤問X時稱，實情是「哥哥」請她吃糖後帶她去玩，其間X稱要如廁，「哥哥」便帶她往商場，但她走了入男廁。他跟入男廁後，沒跟入她的廁格。X否認。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1015/17<br />\n■記者蔡少玲  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n假冒名城業主賣樓　兩男騙292萬候懲<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n路署總工程監督收賄囚半年"},{"pid":"d45f9128af677c7ac6aca43e49a50d38eaa785da","tid":665845,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"Candy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b43351578ab27ba02459334ab278720b29e5361","tid":665845,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"Free candy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a357a0e54aab73f79c4ee26e82e73e3ec5fb23","tid":665845,"uid":47954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"邊個巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd49b1dda029ae7c184a2db2875104635c80d149","tid":665845,"uid":185683,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2df8b4f3fe32a83e1fdc381e2bb34093cf80f696","tid":665845,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"6歲都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ff5cadbe92b58167839f4a637ae39cac6ecfad","tid":665845,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227592dcc7ef0e02150943d28e96e38d00a9402f","tid":665845,"uid":67840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"死變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37f3bde74e04f9822e7f52b37727717c6c5d8b9","tid":665845,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:3